The beautiful sunset&lt;br&gt;
Why does it not last forever?&lt;br&gt;
The majesty of the fall colors,&lt;br&gt;
Why does it not last forever?&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
A lover's embrace&lt;br&gt;
Why does it not last forever?&lt;br&gt;
A divine euphoria&lt;br&gt;
Why does it not last forever?&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;
Craving makes happiness feel like chasing tails&lt;br&gt;
Acceptance makes happiness last forever&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</description><category>poetry</category><guid>https://ganesh-krishnan.github.io/posts/chasing-tails/</guid><pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2020 02:26:56 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>